How to use:

This Simulator calculates values by running each attempt in real-time loop, hence simulating for +20 will take time, up to a few minutes

Keep in mind that the nature of enhancing is pure RNG, so every attempt will result in different values. Nevertheless, it's useful to know the range!

Choose an item from the items list. Once you select an item, some fields will be auto-filled, while others will not

Set remaining empty fields as needed, such as resource prices, protection price, and enhancing skill level

Once all fields are filled, click on the "Start" 1 / 10 / 100 iterations buttons to begin the simulation

You can increase the number of iterations for a more accurate average result by clicking on the 1 / 10 / 100 buttons again

Changing any fields after running iterations will reset everything

What is iterations counter?
Number of times the item reached fromStart At LeveltoStop At Level

What is Coins counter?
How muchcoinsused from the Simulating process

What is Item level?
In Game stat for items that affects multiple calculations, it is auto filled, and advised not to temper it

What is RNG?
Random Number Generators (RNG), a way used to determine random events, such as success rate
